#: src-en/data/events_piracy.xml:76
msgid ""
"data/events_piracy.xml$//eventList[@name=\"PIRATE_CHOICE_RUN\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You quickly fire up your engines and make a break for it. However, it seems "
"to be in vain. They catch up to you effortlessly and power up their weapons."

