"data/events_piracy.xml$//eventList[@name=\"PIRATE_CHOICE_RUN\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You divert all available power to your engines and flee. You caught them "
"off-guard, but they seem to be gaining on you. Luckily you are able to stay "
"out of range long enough to charge the FTL drive."

