msgid ""
"data/events_piracy.xml$//eventList[@name=\"PIRATE_CHOICE_RUN\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"You fire up the engines and try to escape. Their slower ship is unable to "
"keep pace; eventually it gives up and returns to the beacon to await an "
"easier target."

